'''''Tholos''''' was an [[Aramadia-class thrustship|''Aramadia''-class thrustship]].

==History==
The ''Tholos'' fought in the [[Battle of ILC-905]]. Though it outlasted its sister ship, the inexperience of the commander of the ''Tholos'' led to a number of tactical mistakes that led to the destruction the Yevetha fleet and shipyard present at the battle.

